oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Receipt from Johnsonville Quartermasters Office
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Receipt from Assistant Acting Quartermaster's office at Johnsonville (Tenn) dated June 10, 1864 received of Lt. W.H (unreadable) AAQM documenting (12) boxes marked "T.J. Murphy Lieut AQM" 2nd Tenn Mounted Infantry Clifton Tenn. Signed by "T.J. Murphy by C.M. Thompson, Local Sp Agt Treasury Department." At the time of this document Lt. Thomas J. Murphy, was Quartermaster of the 2nd Tenn Mtd. Inf., USA.
